data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3 bed, 2 bath gem - the perfect starter or investment opportunity! Priced to sell, this residence boasts a spacious and inviting atmosphere, complemented by a convenient 3-car garage and paved RV parking, ideal for your adventurous spirit. Situated on a desirable corner lot, the property offers a tranquil and relaxing backyard, creating the perfect retreat for both leisure and entertaining. Enjoy seamless indoor-outdoor living with a sliding door off the master bedroom and dining room, providing easy access to your private outdoor haven. Don't miss out on the chance to make this house your home - a fantastic blend of comfort, functionality, and potential awaits.
